   "body" : "v0.16.0 on Fedora 27 with topicons-plus\r\n\r\n`bitcoin-qt` does not usually close to tray after restore from tray when clicking `x` or right clicking on the application in the taskbar and clicking on close. Using those methods in the case stated, nothing happens.\r\n\r\nTo workaround, a) minimise then restore the gui window or, b) maximise the window, and, then click close or, minimise again and it goes to the tray.",
